title: Bretonnian Keystone Plaza Siege: Dwarfs Epic Last Stand - Total War: WARHAMMER mod Gameplay
description:
Battle Starts: 5:29
Today we are looking at a battle on a custom map on Total War: WARHAMMER called Bretonnian Keystone Plaza.  This is a 3v3 online battle between some awesome factions!  This one comes down to the wire!  Enjoy the battle :D


If you enjoyed the video don't forget to Like and Leave a comment :D
